The following are fees of registration:
1. for a trademark or collective trademark registration, the fee is NT$2,500 per class;
2. for a collective mark or certification mark registration, the fee is NT$2,500.
For those who chose to pay registration fees by two installments and already paid the first installment prior to the enforcement of the articles of this Act amended on May 31, 2011, the following are the amount of second installment shall be paid:
1. for a trademark or collective trademark registration, the amount is NT$1,500 per class;
2. for a collective mark or certification mark registration, the amount is NT$1,500.

The following are fees of division:
1. for division of an application for registration, the fee is NT$2,000 per additional application after the division;
2. for division of a trademark, certification mark, or collective trademark registration, the fee is NT$2,000 per additional registration after the division;
3. for division of a trademark, certification mark, or collective trademark registration prior to the disposition of an opposition, invalidation, or revocation against such trademark or mark become final, NT$2,000 shall be additionally paid in addition to the fee pursuant to preceding subparagraph.

The following are other fees:
1. for amendment or change to particulars in a registration or application for registration, the fee is NT$500 per request; for one request to amendment or change same particulars in multiple registrations or applications for registration, the fee is calculated from each registrations or applications for registration;
2. for a restriction of designated goods or services of a registered trademark, the fee is NT$500;
3. for an entry of a license or sub-license in the Register, the fee is NT$2,000; for one request to an entry of multiple licenses under same conditions in the Register, the fee is calculated from each license; same fee to be paid shall also apply to one request to an entry of multiple sub-licenses under same conditions in the Register;
4. for a removal of a license or sub-license from the Register, the fee is NT$1,000;
5. for an entry of transfer of a registration in the Register, the fee is NT$2,000; for one request to an entry of transfer of multiple registrations under same conditions in the Register, the fee is calculated from each registration;
6. for an entry of a creation of a pledge, the fee is NT$2,000;
7. for an entry of an extinguishment of a pledge, the fee is NT$1,000;
8. for filing an opposition, the fee is NT$4,000 per class;
9. for filing an invalidation, the fee is NT$7,000 per class;
10. for filing a revocation, the fee is NT$7,000 per class;
11. for a request to intervene in an opposition, invalidation or revocation, the fee is NT$2,000;
12. for a request to issue a certified copy of a document, the fee is NT$500;
13. for a request to review official files of a case, the fee is NT$500.
